{
  "stem": "21786.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took us to the military barracks in Prague, and they, after an interrogation and investigation, they shot him in front of us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Very kind of satisfactory tremendously unpleasant feeling, for it was after the war and it should have been handled in-- but the Russian officer asked us if I-- we could name somebody who were fair Germans.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was able to give them three names.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of them was this SS man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know whether he was caught or whether he stayed alive or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one of them was this Mrs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Ruhl from the laundry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she became a mayor of Ruhland in the East-- in East Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Just I sidetracked that I don't know what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, in the-- when it came to bombardment, we were warned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Allied threw leaflets that it will be bombed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At the beginning, you know, when we came to the camp and we have seen this hundreds and hundreds of planes, I mean, over us, we were absolutely thrilled and jubilant.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then simply the last moment we were told, not even by five, run, run, run.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were running out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they took us into-- there were coal mines where they were getting the brown coal for the manufacture of the gas.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was about hundred meters going down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was sand, and we just slid down on our [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] backside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Simply slid down, and we were permitted to enter the adits of the mines.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We are just [INAUDIBLE] the thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Shaking, shaking.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when we came back, it was an absolute bedlam.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I have seen the engine, a locomotive, a train engine sitting in the third floor in the factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There were these huge bombs.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
